      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Burning
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Receives {v1} fire damage at the start of the turn. Affected entity is a
        fire source and adds burning on contact. Prevents wet status by removing
        burning.
      - "\u56DE\u5408\u5F00\u59CB\u65F6\uFF0C\u53D7\u5230 {v1} \u70B9\u706B\u7130\u4F24\u5BB3\u3002\u53D7\u5F71\u54CD\u5355\u4F4D\u53D8\u4E3A\u706B\u6E90\uFF0C\u63A5\u89E6\u65F6\u4E3A\u5BF9\u65B9\u65BD\u52A0\u71C3\u70E7\u72B6\u6001\u3002\u79FB\u9664\u71C3\u70E7\u53EF\u62B5\u6297\u6F6E\u6E7F\u72B6\u6001\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Concealed
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Can't be seen or targeted. Skills that start with the entity concealed have
        100% critical chance and +30% critical damage.
      - "\u65E0\u6CD5\u88AB\u770B\u89C1\u6216\u6210\u4E3A\u76EE\u6807\u3002\u4EE5\u9690\u533F\u72B6\u6001\u5F00\u59CB\u7684\u6280\u80FD\u62E5\u6709
        100% \u66B4\u51FB\u7387\uFF0C\u5E76\u83B7\u5F97 +30% \u66B4\u51FB\u4F24\u5BB3\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Confused
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - The character uses a random skill targeting the nearest available target.
      - "\u89D2\u8272\u4F7F\u7528\u968F\u673A\u6280\u80FD\u653B\u51FB\u8DDD\u79BB\u6700\u8FD1\u7684\u53EF\u653B\u51FB\u76EE\u6807\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Covered
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - The character hides behind adjacent obstacles, decreasing the probability
        to be hit by ranged attacks.
      - "\u89D2\u8272\u9690\u85CF\u5728\u76F8\u90BB\u969C\u788D\u7269\u540E\u65B9\uFF0C\u964D\u4F4E\u88AB\u8FDC\u7A0B\u653B\u51FB\u547D\u4E2D\u7684\u6982\u7387\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_CoveredByVegetation
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - The character hides behind the vegetation, decreasing the probability to
        be hit by ranged attacks.
      - "\u89D2\u8272\u9690\u85CF\u5728\u690D\u88AB\u540E\u65B9\uFF0C\u964D\u4F4E\u88AB\u8FDC\u7A0B\u653B\u51FB\u547D\u4E2D\u7684\u6982\u7387\u3002"
