      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Adds slowed. At the start of the turn, there is a 50% chance of adding confused.
      - "\u65BD\u52A0\u51CF\u901F\u72B6\u6001\u3002\u56DE\u5408\u5F00\u59CB\u65F6\uFF0C\u6709
