      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_InHole
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - If ally, the character receives a small amount of damage and it's removed
        for this combat. If enemy, the character dies.
      - "\u5982\u679C\u662F\u76DF\u53CB\uFF0C\u5219\u89D2\u8272\u53D7\u5230\u5C11\u91CF\u4F24\u5BB3\uFF0C\u5E76\u5728\u672C\u6B21\u6218\u6597\u4E2D\u79FB\u9664\u8BE5\u89D2\u8272\u3002\u5982\u679C\u662F\u654C\u65B9\uFF0C\u5219\u89D2\u8272\u6B7B\u4EA1\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Marked
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Attacks against this entity have {v1}% increased accuracy and {v1}% more
        damage.
      - "\u5BF9\u8BE5\u5355\u4F4D\u53D1\u8D77\u653B\u51FB\u65F6\uFF0C\u547D\u4E2D\u7387\u589E\u52A0
        {v1}%\uFF0C\u4F24\u5BB3\u589E\u52A0 {v1}%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Oiled
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Removes wet status. Vulnerable to fire damage.
      - "\u79FB\u9664\u6F6E\u6E7F\u72B6\u6001\u3002\u5BF9\u706B\u7130\u4F24\u5BB3\u5B58\u5728\u6613\u4F24\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Poisoned
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Receives {v1} damage at the start of the turn and reduces move by {v2}%.
      - "\u56DE\u5408\u5F00\u59CB\u65F6\uFF0C\u53D7\u5230 {v1} \u70B9\u4F24\u5BB3\uFF0C\u4E14\u79FB\u52A8
        {v2}%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Reviving
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - At the end of the turn countdown, the character revives.
      - "\u56DE\u5408\u5012\u8BA1\u65F6\u7ED3\u675F\u65F6\uFF0C\u89D2\u8272\u590D\u6D3B\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Rooted
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Unable to move or be moved.
      - "\u65E0\u6CD5\u79FB\u52A8\u6216\u88AB\u79FB\u52A8\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Sick
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Reduces move by -20%.
      - "\u79FB\u52A8 -20%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Shadowed
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - The entity is cloaked in shadow, whether by night or by shade cast in daylight.
      - "\u8BE5\u5B9E\u4F53\u88AB\u9634\u5F71\u7B3C\u7F69\uFF0C\u65E0\u8BBA\u662F\u591C\u665A\u8FD8\u662F\u767D\u5929\u7684\u9634\u5F71\u4E4B\u4E0B\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Sinking
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Adds rooted. At the end of the turn countdown, the character dies.
      - "\u65BD\u52A0\u88F9\u8DB3\u72B6\u6001\u3002\u56DE\u5408\u5012\u8BA1\u65F6\u7ED3\u675F\u65F6\uFF0C\u89D2\u8272\u6B7B\u4EA1\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Slowed
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Removes -1 AP.
      - "AP -1\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Starving
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Adds slowed.
      - "\u65BD\u52A0\u51CF\u901F\u72B6\u6001\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Stunned
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Unable to perform any action.
      - "\u65E0\u6CD5\u8FDB\u884C\u4EFB\u4F55\u884C\u52A8\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Tainted
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Dark event risk is increased by +3%.
      - "\u6697\u9ED1\u4E8B\u4EF6\u89E6\u53D1\u98CE\u9669 +3%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_TaintedVariant
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - 
      - 
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Taunted
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Forces an enemy to attack or move towards the character who applied this
        status.
      - "\u8FEB\u4F7F\u654C\u4EBA\u653B\u51FB\u6216\u79FB\u52A8\u5230\u65BD\u52A0\u8BE5\u72B6\u6001\u7684\u89D2\u8272\u8EAB\u524D\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Thorned
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Deals {v1} damage, adding bleeding for two turns when hitting, when hit or
        when used as a source to attack.
      - "\u9020\u6210 {v1} \u70B9\u4F24\u5BB3\uFF0C\u5E76\u5728\u547D\u4E2D\u3001\u88AB\u547D\u4E2D\u6216\u4F5C\u4E3A\u653B\u51FB\u6765\u6E90\u65F6\u4E3A\u5BF9\u65B9\u65BD\u52A0\u6D41\u8840\u72B6\u6001\uFF0C\u6301\u7EED\u4E24\u56DE\u5408\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_VitalLink
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Binds two characters. Each receives an extra {v1}% of the damage and healing
        the other takes.
      - "\u7ED1\u5B9A\u4E24\u4E2A\u89D2\u8272\u3002\u6BCF\u4E2A\u89D2\u8272\u6839\u636E\u53E6\u4E00\u4E2A\u89D2\u8272\u53D7\u5230\u7684\u4F24\u5BB3\u548C\u6CBB\u7597\uFF0C\u989D\u5916\u627F\u53D7
        {v1}% \u7684\u76F8\u5E94\u6548\u679C\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Wet
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Vulnerable to electric damage. Resistant to fire damage. Prevents burning
        status by removing wet.
      - "\u5BF9\u7535\u51FB\u4F24\u5BB3\u5B58\u5728\u6613\u4F24\u3002\u5BF9\u706B\u7130\u4F24\u5BB3\u62E5\u6709\u6297\u6027\u3002\u79FB\u9664\u6F6E\u6E7F\u53EF\u62B5\u6297\u71C3\u70E7\u72B6\u6001\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Resilient
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Immune to taunt. Stun and confused status are applied as slowed to this character.
      - "\u514D\u75AB\u5632\u8BBD\u72B6\u6001\u3002\u5BF9\u8BE5\u89D2\u8272\u65BD\u52A0\u7684\u7729\u6655\u548C\u6DF7\u4E71\u72B6\u6001\u5747\u88AB\u89C6\u4E3A\u51CF\u901F\u72B6\u6001\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_CascadingEcho
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Creates a duplicate with the same status effects, but no anomalies, at 50%
        current HP at the end of the turn.
      - "\u5728\u56DE\u5408\u7ED3\u675F\u65F6\u521B\u5EFA\u4E00\u4E2A\u590D\u5236\u4F53\uFF0C\u7EE7\u627F\u76F8\u540C\u7684\u72B6\u6001\u6548\u679C\uFF0C\u4F46\u4E0D\u5305\u542B\u5F02\u5E38\uFF0C\u4E14\u62E5\u6709\u5F53\u524D\u751F\u547D\u503C\u768450%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_RealityBleed
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Creates a duplicate after being hit, with the same current HP.
      - "\u53D7\u5230\u653B\u51FB\u540E\u521B\u5EFA\u4E00\u4E2A\u590D\u5236\u4F53\uFF0C\u62E5\u6709\u76F8\u540C\u7684\u5F53\u524D\u751F\u547D\u503C\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_Phasing
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - One turn is invulnerable (phased), the next is not.
      - "\u4E00\u56DE\u5408\u65E0\u654C\uFF08\u76F8\u4F4D\u5316\uFF09\uFF0C\u4E0B\u4E00\u56DE\u5408\u5219\u4E0D\u662F\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: effects/status_VoidAnchored
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Immune to push and pull.
      - "\u514D\u75AB\u63A8\u62C9\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_armor
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Each armor reduces incoming damage by 1 (up to 3 armor).
      - "\u6BCF 1 \u70B9\u62A4\u7532\u4F1A\u51CF\u5C11 1 \u70B9\u627F\u53D7\u7684\u4F24\u5BB3
        \uFF08\u6700\u591A 3 \u70B9\u62A4\u7532\uFF09\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_cursed
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - 'On end combat: adds blight'
      - "\u6218\u6597\u7ED3\u675F\u65F6\uFF1A\u8150\u5316\u589E\u52A0"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_holy_damage
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Unholy entities are vulnerable to it.
      - "\u53EF\u4F7F\u4EB5\u6E0E\u5355\u4F4D\u6613\u4F24\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_interruption_skill
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - This skill will be performed after the next {value} player's actions.
      - "\u4E0B {value} \u4E2A\u73A9\u5BB6\u884C\u52A8\u4E4B\u540E\uFF0C\u8BE5\u6280\u80FD\u5C06\u88AB\u65BD\u653E\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_lightning_damage
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Wet targets are vulnerable. It's piercing damage.
      - "\u53EF\u4F7F\u6F6E\u6E7F\u76EE\u6807\u6613\u4F24\u3002\u9020\u6210\u7A7F\u900F\u4F24\u5BB3\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_pierce
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Ignores armor and deals damage to both health and barrier simultaneously.
      - "\u65E0\u89C6\u62A4\u7532\uFF0C\u5E76\u540C\u65F6\u5BF9\u751F\u547D\u503C\u548C\u62A4\u76FE\u9020\u6210\u4F24\u5BB3\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_unstoppableDamage
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Ignores armor and barrier.
      - "\u65E0\u89C6\u62A4\u7532\u548C\u62A4\u76FE\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_propel
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Pushes an entity across the ground or through the air. The distance depends
        on the propeller's strength and the entity's size.
      - "\u5728\u5730\u9762\u6216\u7A7A\u4E2D\u63A8\u52A8\u5355\u4F4D\u3002\u8DDD\u79BB\u7531\u63A8\u52A8\u8005\u7684\u529B\u91CF\u548C\u5355\u4F4D\u7684\u5927\u5C0F\u51B3\u5B9A\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_purify
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Heals or deals piercing holy damage to unholy.
      - "\u83B7\u5F97\u6CBB\u7597\uFF0C\u6216\u5BF9\u4EB5\u6E0E\u8005\u9020\u6210\u7A7F\u900F\u795E\u5723\u4F24\u5BB3\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_resistance_damage
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Receives 50% less damage.
      - "\u627F\u53D7\u7684\u4F24\u5BB3\u51CF\u5C11 50%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_resistance_status
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Chance to resist status by 50%.
      - "\u6709 50% \u51E0\u7387\u83B7\u5F97\u72B6\u6001\u6297\u6027\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_shred
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Removes armor.
      - "\u79FB\u9664\u62A4\u7532\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_strength
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Strength determines the distance and damage dealt when propelling or moving
        other entities, if possible.
      - "\u529B\u91CF\u51B3\u5B9A\u5728\u63A8\u52A8\u6216\u79FB\u52A8\u5176\u4ED6\u5355\u4F4D\u65F6\uFF08\u82E5\u53EF\u884C\uFF09\u6240\u9020\u6210\u7684\u8DDD\u79BB\u548C\u4F24\u5BB3\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_temporary_armor
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Prevents the next point of damage and then disappears.
      - "\u5438\u6536\u4E0B\u4E00\u6B21 1 \u70B9\u4F24\u5BB3\uFF0C\u968F\u540E\u6D88\u5931\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_threat
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Determines the extra probability of being attacked.
      - "\u51B3\u5B9A\u6267\u884C\u6307\u5411\u6027\u653B\u51FB\u65F6\u7684\u547D\u4E2D\u7387\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_vulnerable
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Receives +50% damage.
      - "\u627F\u53D7\u7684\u4F24\u5BB3\u589E\u52A0 50%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_chain
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - The damage and effects dealt are propagated X times to the nearest relevant
        target.
      - "\u9020\u6210\u7684\u4F24\u5BB3\u548C\u6548\u679C\u5411\u6700\u8FD1\u7684\u76F8\u5173\u76EE\u6807\u4F20\u9012
        X \u6B21\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_blight
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A measurement for the hero's corruption. At 25/50/75 blight, the hero becomes
        tainted/deranged/fractured, adding different negative modifiers.
      - "\u7528\u4E8E\u8861\u91CF\u82F1\u96C4\u7684\u8150\u5316\u7A0B\u5EA6\u3002\u5F53\u67AF\u840E\u8FBE\u5230
        25/50/75 \u65F6\uFF0C\u82F1\u96C4\u5C06\u5206\u522B\u53D8\u4E3A\u6C61\u67D3\u3001\u5931\u5E8F\u6216\u7834\u788E\u72B6\u6001\uFF0C\u5E76\u83B7\u5F97\u4E0D\u540C\u7684\u8D1F\u9762\u4FEE\u6B63\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_unshreddable_armor
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Each unshreddable armor reduces incoming damage by 1. It can't be shredded.
      - "\u6BCF\u6709 1 \u70B9\u4E0D\u53EF\u7834\u9664\u62A4\u7532\uFF0C\u4FBF\u4F1A\u51CF\u5C11
        1 \u70B9\u627F\u53D7\u7684\u4F24\u5BB3\u3002\u65E0\u6CD5\u7834\u9664\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_deathWard
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Prevents death and revives the character with 1 HP and -100% threat for one
        turn.
      - "\u89D2\u8272\u53D7\u5230\u81F4\u547D\u4F24\u5BB3\u65F6\uFF0C\u4F7F\u5176\u514D\u4E8E\u6B7B\u4EA1\uFF08\u5373\u4EE5
        1 \u70B9\u751F\u547D\u503C\u590D\u6D3B\uFF09\uFF0C\u540C\u65F6\u4F7F\u5176\u5A01\u80C1\u503C\u5728\u4E00\u56DE\u5408\u5185
        -100%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_quickstep
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A small free movement in any direction.
      - "\u5411\u4EFB\u610F\u65B9\u5411\u514D\u8D39\u79FB\u52A8\u4E00\u5C0F\u6BB5\u8DDD\u79BB\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_deathWardHeroes
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Prevents a hero's death, reviving the character with 1 HP and -100% threat
        for one turn.
      - "\u9632\u6B62\u4E00\u540D\u82F1\u96C4\u6B7B\u4EA1\uFF0C\u4F7F\u8BE5\u89D2\u8272\u4EE5
        1 \u70B9\u751F\u547D\u503C\u590D\u6D3B\uFF0C\u5E76\u5728\u4E00\u56DE\u5408\u5185\u5A01\u80C1\u503C
        -100%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_deathWardCrystal
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Prevents crystal's death, reviving it with 1 HP and -100% threat for one
        turn.
      - "\u9632\u6B62\u6C34\u6676\u6B7B\u4EA1\uFF0C\u4F7F\u5176\u4EE5 1 \u70B9\u751F\u547D\u503C\u590D\u6D3B\uFF0C\u5E76\u5728\u4E00\u56DE\u5408\u5185\u5A01\u80C1\u503C
        -100%\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: combat/action_accuracy
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Determines the hit chance when performing targeted attacks. The hit chance
        is affected by the size of the target, obstacles in the trajectory, target's
        dodge stat and if it's covered. Hit chance also affects critical chance.
      - "\u51B3\u5B9A\u6267\u884C\u6307\u5411\u6027\u653B\u51FB\u65F6\u7684\u547D\u4E2D\u7387\u3002\u547D\u4E2D\u7387\u4F1A\u53D7\u5230\u76EE\u6807\u4F53\u578B\u3001\u653B\u51FB\u8F68\u8FF9\u4E0A\u7684\u969C\u788D\u7269\u3001\u76EE\u6807\u7684\u95EA\u907F\u5C5E\u6027\u4EE5\u53CA\u662F\u5426\u5904\u4E8E\u63A9\u62A4\u72B6\u6001\u7684\u5F71\u54CD\u3002\u547D\u4E2D\u7387\u540C\u65F6\u4E5F\u4F1A\u5F71\u54CD\u66B4\u51FB\u7387\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
