      - "<random_adventurer>\u8DD1\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/corruptionLaments
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - <target> stayed all night lamenting, the blight is taking its toll.
      - "<target>\u6574\u591C\u54C0\u53F9\uFF0C\u8F97\u8F6C\u96BE\u7720\u2014\u2014\u8150\u5316\u6B63\u5728\u4FB5\u8680\u751F\u547D\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/corruptionDestructs
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - <target> awakes in the middle of the night and destroys some goods. Then
        goes back to sleep as nothing happened.
      - "<target>\u534A\u591C\u9192\u6765\uFF0C\u6BC1\u6389\u4E86\u4E00\u4E9B\u8D27\u7269\uFF0C\u7136\u540E\u53C8\u82E5\u65E0\u5176\u4E8B\u5730\u56DE\u53BB\u7761\u89C9\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/corruptionAttacks
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - <target> awakes and attacks <random_adventurer_target> and fight.
      - "<target>\u9192\u6765\u540E\u653B\u51FB\u4E86<random_adventurer_target>\uFF0C\u53CC\u65B9\u6253\u4E86\u8D77\u6765\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/corruptionSuicide
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - In a moment of lucidity, <target> took its own life. The burden of the blight
        was too much.
      - "<target>\u5728\u77ED\u6682\u6E05\u9192\u7684\u65F6\u523B\uFF0C\u7ED3\u675F\u4E86\u81EA\u5DF1\u7684\u751F\u547D\u3002\u8150\u5316\u9020\u6210\u7684\u75DB\u82E6\u5B9E\u5728\u96BE\u4EE5\u627F\u53D7\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskBandits
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Two bandits tried to rob last night, luckily they didn't expect to be noticed
        and they were killed. The combat bring some wounds though.
      - "\u6628\u665A\uFF0C\u6709\u4E24\u4E2A\u5F3A\u76D7\u4F01\u56FE\u6253\u52AB\uFF0C\u5E78\u597D\u4ED6\u4EEC\u8B66\u60D5\u6027\u4E0D\u9AD8\uFF0C\u5DF2\u7ECF\u88AB\u5E72\u6389\u4E86\u3002\u4E0D\u8FC7\uFF0C\u8FD9\u573A\u6253\u6597\u5374\u7ED9\u5192\u9669\u8005\u7559\u4E0B\u4E86\u4E00\u4E9B\u4F24\u53E3\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskDemonAssassin
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A demon visited the campfire, assassinating an adventurer before being killed
        by the others.
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u6076\u9B54\u6765\u5230\u7BDD\u706B\u65C1\uFF0C\u6697\u6740\u4E86\u4E00\u4E2A\u5192\u9669\u8005\uFF0C\u4E4B\u540E\u88AB\u5176\u4ED6\u4EBA\u5E72\u6389\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskCreepingMist
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A creeping mist visited the campfire all night.
      - "\u4E00\u6574\u665A\uFF0C\u7BDD\u706B\u90FD\u88AB\u4E00\u56E2\u9634\u68EE\u68EE\u7684\u8FF7\u96FE\u6240\u7B3C\u7F69\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskDemonVisit
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - An adventurer received the terrifying visist of a demon during the night.
        Was it a dream or real?
      - "\u5192\u9669\u8005\u5728\u591C\u95F4\u9047\u5230\u4E86\u53EF\u6015\u7684\u6076\u9B54\u3002\u4F46\u90A3\u7A76\u7ADF\u662F\u68A6\u5883\uFF0C\u8FD8\u662F\u73B0\u5B9E\uFF1F"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskEnemyAdventurers
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A band of corrupted enemies tried to steal the crystal. The battle was hard
        but looks like the crystal reacted and helped the adventurers to win it.
      - "\u4E00\u7FA4\u8150\u5316\u654C\u4EBA\u8BD5\u56FE\u5077\u8D70\u6C34\u6676\u3002\u5728\u6FC0\u70C8\u7684\u6218\u6597\u4E2D\uFF0C\u6C34\u6676\u4F3C\u4E4E\u51FA\u73B0\u4E86\u53CD\u5E94\uFF0C\u5E76\u6700\u7EC8\u5E2E\u52A9\u5192\u9669\u8005\u4EEC\u8D62\u5F97\u4E86\u80DC\u5229\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskFoodSteal
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A very silent creature stole food. Was it a wild raccoon? Maybe a lost and
        hungry kid?
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u5C0F\u4E1C\u897F\u6084\u65E0\u58F0\u606F\u5730\u5077\u8D70\u4E86\u98DF\u7269\u3002\u4F1A\u662F\u91CE\u5916\u7684\u6D63\u718A\u5417\uFF1F\u53C8\u6216\u8005\u662F\u4E2A\u9965\u80A0\u8F98\u8F98\u7684\u8FF7\u8DEF\u5B69\u5B50\uFF1F"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskIneptThief
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - An inept thief sneak up during the night and stole some resources.
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u7B28\u62D9\u7684\u5C0F\u5077\u591C\u91CC\u6478\u4E86\u8FDB\u6765\uFF0C\u5077\u8D70\u4E86\u4E00\u4E9B\u8D44\u6E90\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskThief
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A thief stole an equipment piece ({[RANDOM_ITEM]}). The trail seems to go
        in opposite direction to the rift. So long precious item.
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u5C0F\u5077\u7A83\u53D6\u4E86\u4E00\u4EF6\u88C5\u5907({[RANDOM_ITEM]})\uFF0C\u770B\u8E2A\u8FF9\uFF0C\u5927\u6982\u662F\u5F80\u88C2\u9699\u7684\u53CD\u65B9\u5411\u53BB\u4E86\u3002\u6240\u4EE5......\u53EA\u597D\u8DDF\u5B9D\u8D1D\u7269\u54C1\u8BF4\u518D\u89C1\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskWildDogs
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Some wild dogs raided the encampment, doing some damage and destroying some
        good in the process.
      - "\u51E0\u53EA\u91CE\u72AC\u88AD\u51FB\u4E86\u8425\u5730\uFF0C\u9020\u6210\u4E86\u4E00\u4E9B\u7834\u574F\uFF0C\u8FD8\u6BC1\u6389\u4E86\u4E00\u4E9B\u8D27\u7269\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskRiftGases
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - The proximity to the rift bring some of its corrupting gases during the night.
      - "\u8DDD\u79BB\u88C2\u9699\u8D8A\u6765\u8D8A\u8FD1\uFF0C\u591C\u95F4\u5F00\u59CB\u51FA\u73B0\u4E00\u4E9B\u8150\u5316\u6C14\u4F53\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskNightViper
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A poisonous night viper bit one of the adventurers.
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u5192\u9669\u8005\u88AB\u591C\u95F4\u51FA\u6CA1\u7684\u6BD2\u86C7\u54AC\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskMountainWinds
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A mountain wind blew everything away, including all the map information.
      - "\u4E00\u9635\u5C71\u98CE\u628A\u6240\u6709\u4E1C\u897F\u90FD\u5439\u98DE\u4E86\uFF0C\u5305\u62EC\u6240\u6709\u5730\u56FE\u8D44\u6599\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskWhisperingShadows
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Mysterious whispers fill the air, making very hard to sleep well for some.
      - "\u7A7A\u6C14\u4E2D\u5F25\u6F2B\u7740\u795E\u79D8\u4F4E\u8BED\uFF0C\u5BFC\u81F4\u4E00\u4E9B\u4EBA\u5F88\u96BE\u5165\u7761\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskTimeDistortion
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Somehow, in the campfire area, the night turned into morning in an instant.
      - "\u4E0D\u77E5\u600E\u4E48\u56DE\u4E8B\uFF0C\u5728\u7BDD\u706B\u533A\u57DF\u8303\u56F4\u5185\uFF0C\u9ED1\u591C\u77AC\u95F4\u53D8\u4E3A\u4E86\u6E05\u6668\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskEnemyAdventurersAttack
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Enemy adventurers attacked the camp.
      - "\u654C\u65B9\u5192\u9669\u8005\u88AD\u51FB\u4E86\u8425\u5730\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskBoars
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A group of boars ate some food. Luckily they run away when they noticed they
        were not alone.
      - "\u4E00\u7FA4\u5C71\u732A\u5403\u6389\u4E86\u90E8\u5206\u98DF\u7269\u3002\u6240\u5E78\u5B83\u4EEC\u4E00\u6CE8\u610F\u5230\u6709\u4EBA\u5C31\u8DD1\u8D70\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskBear
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - An enraged bear attacked the party while sleeping, damaging an adventurer
        before dying.
      - "\u4E00\u5934\u66B4\u6012\u7684\u718A\u5728\u5927\u5BB6\u719F\u7761\u65F6\u88AD\u51FB\u4E86\u961F\u4F0D\u3002\u867D\u7136\u5B83\u88AB\u5F53\u573A\u51FB\u6BD9\uFF0C\u4F46\u8FD8\u662F\u6709\u4E00\u540D\u5192\u9669\u8005\u56E0\u6B64\u53D7\u4F24\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskCrystalAddicts
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A corrupted earthglass addict damaged the crystal until the adventurers realized
        what was happening.
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u75F4\u8FF7\u5927\u5730\u6C34\u6676\u7684\u8150\u5316\u8005\u635F\u574F\u4E86\u6C34\u6676\u3002\u8FC7\u4E86\u597D\u4E00\u4F1A\u513F\uFF0C\u5192\u9669\u8005\u4EEC\u624D\u53CD\u5E94\u8FC7\u6765\u53D1\u751F\u4E86\u4EC0\u4E48\u4E8B\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskExpertThief
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - One of the adventurers is missing one equipment ({[RANDOM_ITEM]}). An expert
        thief.
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u5192\u9669\u8005\u4E22\u5931\u4E86\u4E00\u4EF6\u88C5\u5907({[RANDOM_ITEM]})\u3002\u770B\u6765\u662F\u4E2A\u8001\u624B\u5077\u7684\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskLaments
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Not knowing the source, what seemed haunting human laments were heard during
        all night, the party didn't rest at all.
      - "\u4E00\u6574\u665A\u90FD\u80FD\u542C\u89C1\u8426\u7ED5\u4E0D\u53BB\u7684\u54C0\u53F9\uFF0C\u4E5F\u4E0D\u77E5\u9053\u4ECE\u54EA\u91CC\u4F20\u6765\u7684\uFF0C\u961F\u4F0D\u6210\u5458\u6839\u672C\u6CA1\u529E\u6CD5\u4F11\u606F\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/riskZombies
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A horde of zombies stumbled with the campfire. After a chaotic battle the
        adventurers survived.
      - "\u4E00\u7FA4\u50F5\u5C38\u8E09\u8DC4\u5730\u6251\u8FDB\u7BDD\u706B\u3002\u4E00\u573A\u6DF7\u6218\u540E\uFF0C\u5192\u9669\u8005\u4EEC\u6D3B\u4E86\u4E0B\u6765\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/starvingComplains
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - The hunger made an adventurer complain several times during night.
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u9965\u80A0\u8F98\u8F98\u7684\u5192\u9669\u8005\u5728\u591C\u95F4\u62B1\u6028\u4E86\u597D\u591A\u6B21\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: dark events/starvingHunt
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
