      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Now we are doing this together. We are one.'
      - "{positive}\u73B0\u5728\uFF0C\u8BA9\u6211\u4EEC\u4E00\u8D77\u9762\u5BF9\u56F0\u96BE\u5427\u3002\u6211\u4EEC\u662F\u4E00\u4E2A\u96C6\u4F53\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v1_8
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}Touching. Truly. Tell me, Xander... how many times have you tried?
        How many times have you failed?'
      - "{pensive}\u771F\u611F\u4EBA\u554A\u3002\u6851\u5FB7\u5C14\uFF0C\u8DDF\u6211\u8BF4\u8BF4......\u4F60\u52AA\u529B\u4E86\u591A\u5C11\u6B21\uFF1F\u53C8\u5931\u8D25\u4E86\u591A\u5C11\u6B21\uFF1F"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v1_9
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{triumph}I don''t dwell on failure. Only on what comes next.'
      - "{triumph}\u6211\u4E0D\u4F1A\u5728\u5931\u8D25\u4E2D\u6C89\u6CA6\u3002\u6211\u53EA\u4F1A\u4E00\u5F80\u65E0\u524D\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v1_10
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}And yet, the path before you does not change. The future has already
        been written.'
      - "{pensive}\u53EF\u60DC\u554A\uFF0C\u4F60\u7684\u524D\u8DEF\u4E0D\u4F1A\u6539\u53D8\u3002\u4F60\u7684\u672A\u6765\u5DF2\u7ECF\u6CE8\u5B9A\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v1_11
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}Every choice you make, every spell you cast... all of it leads
        here. To me. And to your inevitable failure.'
      - "{pensive}\u4F60\u505A\u51FA\u7684\u6BCF\u4E2A\u9009\u62E9\uFF0C\u65BD\u653E\u7684\u6BCF\u4E2A\u6CD5\u672F......\u90FD\u662F\u4E3A\u4E86\u6765\u5230\u8FD9\u91CC\u4E0E\u6211\u8F83\u91CF\uFF0C\u7136\u540E\u54C1\u5C1D\u4F60\u6CE8\u5B9A\u7684\u5931\u8D25\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v1_12
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{rage}Then I''ll rewrite fate myself.'
      - "{rage}\u90A3\u5C31\u7531\u6211\u4EB2\u81EA\u6539\u5199\u547D\u8FD0\u597D\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v1_13
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}Ah... such arrogance. Such conviction. It''s entertaining, really.
        Very well. Prove me wrong, little timekeeper.'
      - "{pensive}\u54C8......\u5982\u6B64\u72C2\u5984\u81EA\u5927\uFF0C\u771F\u662F\u53EF\u7B11\u3002\u6765\u5427\uFF0C\u5FAE\u4E0D\u8DB3\u9053\u7684\u65F6\u95F4\u5B88\u62A4\u8005\uFF0C\u6709\u672C\u4E8B\u5C31\u8BC1\u660E\u6211\u770B\u9519\u4F60\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v2_1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Xander?! You made it!'
      - "{positive}\u6851\u5FB7\u5C14\uFF1F\uFF01\u4F60\u6210\u529F\u4E86\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v2_2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - "{pensive}Still surprised? How delightful. Even now, you don't remember.
        Not the screams. Not the endings. Just fresh hope\u2014every time."
      - "{pensive}\u7ADF\u7136\u8FD8\u4F1A\u611F\u5230\u610F\u5916\uFF1F\u6709\u8DA3\u6781\u4E86\u3002\u54EA\u6015\u6B7B\u5230\u4E34\u5934\uFF0C\u4ECD\u65E7\u4E0D\u957F\u8BB0\u6027\u3002\u6BCF\u6B21\u4F60\u90FD\u5FD8\u8BB0\u75DB\u82E6\u7684\u8FC7\u7A0B\u548C\u7ED3\u5C40\uFF0C\u5012\u53EA\u8BB0\u5F97\u5168\u65B0\u7684\u5E0C\u671B\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v2_3
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}Do you feel it, Xander? The weight of your failures? The inevitable
        end you cannot avoid?'
      - "{pensive}\u6851\u5FB7\u5C14\uFF0C\u5C1D\u5230\u5931\u8D25\u7684\u6ECB\u5473\u4E86\u5417\uFF1F\u8FD9\u662F\u4F60\u6CE8\u5B9A\u7684\u7ED3\u5C40\uFF0C\u4F60\u65E0\u80FD\u4E3A\u529B\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v2_4
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}You''re wrong. I''m not going to stop. You''re just trying to
        crush my will.'
      - "{positive}\u4F60\u9519\u4E86\u3002\u6211\u4E0D\u4F1A\u653E\u5F03\u3002\u4F60\u4E0D\u8FC7\u662F\u60F3\u538B\u57AE\u6211\u7684\u610F\u5FD7\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v2_5
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Xander''s right! We will keep on fighting!'
      - "{positive}\u6851\u5FB7\u5C14\u8BF4\u7684\u6CA1\u9519\uFF01\u6211\u4EEC\u8981\u7EE7\u7EED\u6218\u6597\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v2_6
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{rage}You''re not strong enough. No one is. I am the end of every story.
        Your struggle is meaningless.'
      - "{rage}\u4F60\u4EEC\u4E0D\u591F\u5F3A\u3002\u8C01\u4E5F\u65E0\u6CD5\u6218\u80DC\u6211\u3002\u6240\u6709\u4EBA\u5728\u6211\u9762\u524D\u90FD\u5C06\u6B62\u6B65\u3002\u4F60\u4EEC\u518D\u600E\u4E48\u6323\u624E\u4E5F\u6CA1\u7528\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v2_7
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - "{positive}We will keep fighting\u2014because that's what matters!"
      - "{positive}\u6211\u4EEC\u8981\u7EE7\u7EED\u6218\u6597\uFF01\u8FD9\u624D\u662F\u6700\u91CD\u8981\u7684\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}So, you think the crystal will close the Rift, do you? How quaint.
        You''re deluded if you believe that.'
      - "{pensive}\u770B\u6765\uFF0C\u4F60\u4EEC\u4EE5\u4E3A\u6C34\u6676\u53EF\u4EE5\u5173\u95ED\u88C2\u9699\uFF1F\u771F\u662F\u5947\u4E86\u3002\u4F60\u4EEC\u82E5\u662F\u76F8\u4FE1\u8FD9\u65E0\u7A3D\u4E4B\u8C08\uFF0C\u90A3\u624D\u662F\u771F\u7684\u88AB\u8FF7\u60D1\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{taunt}Whoa! Xander!'
      - "{taunt}\u54C7\u5662\uFF01\u6851\u5FB7\u5C14\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_3
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Don''t listen to him. He''s trying to get into your heads. That''s
        what he does. Resist it. Stay focused.'
      - "{positive}\u522B\u542C\u4ED6\u7684\u3002\u4ED6\u6700\u64C5\u957F\u86CA\u60D1\u5FC3\u667A\u3002\u4FDD\u6301\u4E13\u6CE8\uFF0C\u522B\u8BA9\u81EA\u5DF1\u53D7\u5230\u52A8\u6447\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_4
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{rage}And you...'
      - "{rage}\u81F3\u4E8E\u4F60......"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_5
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{rage}We''ll use the crystal to stop you and end this invasion.'
      - "{rage}\u6211\u4EEC\u4F1A\u7528\u6C34\u6676\u5236\u670D\u4F60\uFF0C\u7EC8\u7ED3\u8FD9\u6B21\u5165\u4FB5\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_6
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}Xander... you can''t. No one can.'
      - "{pensive}\u6851\u5FB7\u5C14......\u4F60\u505A\u4E0D\u5230\u3002\u6CA1\u4EBA\u80FD\u505A\u5230\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_7
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}The Rift is already part of this world. Nothing can undo it.'
      - "{pensive}\u88C2\u9699\u5DF2\u7ECF\u4E0E\u8FD9\u4E2A\u4E16\u754C\u878D\u4E3A\u4E00\u4F53\uFF0C\u4EFB\u8C01\u90FD\u65E0\u6CD5\u9006\u8F6C\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_8
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{triumph}We''ll see. I won''t let you win. The Rift will close, and you
        will fall.'
      - "{triumph}\u7B49\u7740\u77A7\u3002\u6211\u4E0D\u4F1A\u8BA9\u4F60\u5F97\u901E\u7684\u3002\u88C2\u9699\u5C06\u4F1A\u5173\u95ED\uFF0C\u800C\u4F60\u4E5F\u5C06\u4E00\u8D25\u6D82\u5730\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_v3_9
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Let''s show him how it''s done.'
      - "{positive}\u6765\u5427\uFF0C\u7ED9\u4ED6\u70B9\u989C\u8272\u77A7\u77A7\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{rage}What are you doing here?!'
      - "{rage}\u4F60\u600E\u4E48\u5728\u8FD9\uFF1F\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}I was never far. I had to be sure you''d reach this point.'
      - "{pensive}\u6211\u4ECE\u6765\u6CA1\u6709\u8D70\u8FDC\u3002\u6211\u5FC5\u987B\u786E\u4FDD\u4F60\u4EEC\u6765\u5230\u8FD9\u91CC\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_3
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}Ah. That look again... surprise.'
      - "{pensive}\u54C8\u3002\u53C8\u9732\u51FA\u4E00\u526F......\u60CA\u8BB6\u7684\u8868\u60C5\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_4
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}It was amusing the first dozen times. Now it''s just irritating.'
      - "{pensive}\u8D77\u521D\u51E0\u6B21\u8FD8\u633A\u6709\u8DA3\u3002\u4F46\u8FD9\u4E00\u6B21\u5DF2\u7ECF\u4EE4\u6211\u611F\u5230\u538C\u70E6\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_5
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}You''ve heard it all before, haven''t you?'
      - "{pensive}\u60F3\u5FC5\u4F60\u6B64\u524D\u90FD\u542C\u8BF4\u4E86\u5427\uFF1F"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_6
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}You''ll fall like the others, and your magic won''t change a thing.
        How long will you keep up this charade?'
      - "{pensive}\u4F60\u4F1A\u8DDF\u5176\u4ED6\u4EBA\u4E00\u6837\u5931\u8D25\uFF0C\u4F60\u7684\u9B54\u6CD5\u4EC0\u4E48\u4E5F\u6539\u53D8\u4E0D\u4E86\u3002\u6240\u4EE5\uFF0C\u4F60\u8FD8\u8981\u88C5\u6A21\u4F5C\u6837\u5230\u4EC0\u4E48\u65F6\u5019\uFF1F"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_7
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Don''t listen to him. He wants doubt. Don''t give it to him.'
      - "{positive}\u522B\u542C\u4ED6\u7684\u3002\u4ED6\u5E0C\u671B\u4F60\u4EEC\u6000\u7591\u81EA\u5DF1\uFF0C\u4E0D\u8981\u5982\u4ED6\u7684\u613F\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_8
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}We''ll keep fighting until the very last moment, because he''s
        wrong. This is not over.'
      - "{positive}\u6211\u4EEC\u4F1A\u4E00\u76F4\u6218\u6597\u5230\u6700\u540E\u4E00\u523B\uFF0C\u56E0\u4E3A\u4ED6\u9519\u4E86\u3002\u6211\u4EEC\u4E0D\u4F1A\u6B62\u6B65\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_9
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}It is over, Xander. You''ve always known it. Deep down, you know
        there''s no rewriting the end.'
      - "{pensive}\u90FD\u7ED3\u675F\u4E86\uFF0C\u6851\u5FB7\u5C14\u3002\u4F60\u5FC3\u91CC\u4E00\u76F4\u5F88\u6E05\u695A\uFF0C\u4F60\u660E\u77E5\u7ED3\u5C40\u65E0\u6CD5\u6539\u5199\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_10
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{rage}I''ll never accept that. This time, I will make a difference.'
      - "{rage}\u6211\u7EDD\u4E0D\u63A5\u53D7\u3002\u8FD9\u6B21\u6211\u8981\u6539\u53D8\u7ED3\u5C40\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr1_11
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Let''s do him a favour and put an end to his irritation, shall
        we?'
      - "{positive}\u6765\u5427\uFF0C\u6211\u4EEC\u5E2E\u4ED6\u4E00\u628A\uFF0C\u628A\u8FD9\u4E2A\u8BA8\u538C\u9B3C\u5E72\u6389\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{taunt}Xander? What are you doing here?'
      - "{taunt}\u6851\u5FB7\u5C14\uFF1F\u4F60\u600E\u4E48\u5728\u8FD9\u513F\uFF1F"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - "{positive}I was never far. I told you\u2014we'd face this together."
      - "{positive}\u6211\u4ECE\u6765\u6CA1\u6709\u8D70\u8FDC\u3002\u6211\u8DDF\u4F60\u4EEC\u8BF4\u8FC7\uFF0C\u6211\u4EEC\u8981\u4E00\u8D77\u9762\u5BF9\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_3
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}You think you''ve learned something new, but all you''re doing
        is following a path that leads to me.'
      - "{pensive}\u4F60\u4EEC\u81EA\u4EE5\u4E3A\u6709\u6240\u957F\u8FDB\uFF0C\u4F46\u5176\u5B9E\u4E0D\u8BBA\u4F60\u4EEC\u505A\u4EC0\u4E48\uFF0C\u6700\u540E\u90FD\u8981\u9762\u5BF9\u6211\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_4
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}There''s nothing you can do to change it.'
      - "{pensive}\u518D\u600E\u4E48\u6323\u624E\uFF0C\u7ED3\u5C40\u90FD\u65E0\u6CD5\u6539\u53D8\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_5
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{rage}I don''t believe that. I''ll break this loop, no matter what.'
      - "{rage}\u6211\u4E0D\u4FE1\u3002\u65E0\u8BBA\u5982\u4F55\uFF0C\u6211\u90FD\u8981\u6253\u7834\u547D\u8FD0\u7684\u8F6E\u56DE\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_6
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}You think your magic will change destiny?'
      - "{pensive}\u4F60\u4EE5\u4E3A\u9760\u9B54\u6CD5\u5C31\u80FD\u9006\u5929\u6539\u547D\uFF1F"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_7
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - "{pensive}All your power, all your knowledge\u2014none of it will matter.
        The future has been written."
      - "{pensive}\u4F60\u6240\u6709\u7684\u529B\u91CF\u548C\u77E5\u8BC6\u90FD\u65E0\u5173\u7D27\u8981\u2014\u2014\u672A\u6765\u5DF2\u7ECF\u6CE8\u5B9A\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_8
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}The future is still in motion. You''re just another obstacle in
        our way.'
      - "{positive}\u672A\u6765\u4ECD\u5728\u53D8\u5E7B\u3002\u4F60\u53EA\u662F\u6211\u4EEC\u5F81\u9014\u4E0A\u7684\u4E00\u9897\u7ECA\u811A\u77F3\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: arcs/demonKorghul_start_a1_vr2_9
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
