    - Term: tutorial/SCENE 1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - 
      - 
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_brawler
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - It's your turn. Each hero has 2 Action Points (AP) to move or unleash their
        skills.
      - "\u8F6E\u5230\u4F60\u7684\u56DE\u5408\u4E86\u3002\u6BCF\u4F4D\u82F1\u96C4\u90FD\u6709
        2 AP\uFF08\u884C\u52A8\u70B9\uFF09\uFF0C\u53EF\u4EE5\u7528\u6765\u79FB\u52A8\u4F4D\u7F6E\u6216\u91CA\u653E\u6280\u80FD\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_uppercut
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - The Uppercut skill costs 1 AP. Click on it.
      - "\u4E0A\u52FE\u62F3\u6280\u80FD\u4F1A\u6D88\u8017 1 AP\u3002\u70B9\u51FB\u6280\u80FD\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_enemy
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Most melee skills include a free move. Confirm the target.
      - "\u5927\u591A\u6570\u8FD1\u6218\u6280\u80FD\u90FD\u5305\u542B\u4E00\u6B21\u514D\u8D39\u884C\u52A8\u3002\u786E\u5B9A\u653B\u51FB\u76EE\u6807\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_shot1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Use the Bolt Shot skill. It costs 1 green AP. Skills that use red APs end
        the hero's turn.
      - "\u4F7F\u7528\u5F29\u7BAD\u5C04\u51FB\u6280\u80FD\uFF0C\u8BE5\u6280\u80FD\u6D88\u8017
        1 \u7EFF\u8272 AP\u3002\u4F7F\u7528\u6D88\u8017\u7EA2\u8272 AP \u7684\u6280\u80FD\u540E\uFF0C\u82F1\u96C4\u56DE\u5408\u7ED3\u675F\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_shot2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Confirm the target.
      - "\u786E\u5B9A\u653B\u51FB\u76EE\u6807\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_hunter1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Hubert still has 1 AP. Use the Dog Attack skill.
      - "\u4F11\u4F2F\u7279\u8FD8\u5269 1 AP\u3002\u4F7F\u7528\u730E\u72AC\u51FA\u51FB\u6280\u80FD\u5427\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_hunter2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Confirm the target.
      - "\u786E\u5B9A\u653B\u51FB\u76EE\u6807\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_pathfinding1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Click the Move skill to activate pathfinding.
      - "\u70B9\u51FB\u79FB\u52A8\u6280\u80FD\uFF0C\u542F\u7528\u5BFB\u8DEF\u529F\u80FD\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_pathfinding2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Move Armand to the marked spot.
      - "\u5C06\u963F\u66FC\u5FB7\u79FB\u52A8\u81F3\u6807\u8BB0\u4F4D\u7F6E\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_telekinesis1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Use the Telekinesis skill to throw the barrel at the enemies.
      - "\u4F7F\u7528\u5FF5\u529B\u64CD\u63A7\u6280\u80FD\uFF0C\u5C06\u6876\u6254\u5411\u654C\u4EBA\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat1_telekinesis2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Confirm the target and finish off all the enemies!
      - "\u786E\u5B9A\u653B\u51FB\u76EE\u6807\uFF0C\u6D88\u706D\u6240\u6709\u654C\u4EBA\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - 
      - 
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_intro1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Heroes can use obstacles as cover, making ranged attacks against them harder.
        Click the Move skill to activate pathfinding.
      - "\u82F1\u96C4\u53EF\u4EE5\u5229\u7528\u969C\u788D\u7269\u505A\u63A9\u62A4\uFF0C\u4F7F\u654C\u4EBA\u7684\u8FDC\u7A0B\u653B\u51FB\u66F4\u96BE\u547D\u4E2D\u3002\u70B9\u51FB\u79FB\u52A8\u6280\u80FD\uFF0C\u542F\u7528\u5BFB\u8DEF\u529F\u80FD\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_intro2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Move Hubert to the marked position to take cover.
      - "\u5C06\u4F11\u4F2F\u7279\u79FB\u81F3\u6807\u8BB0\u4F4D\u7F6E\uFF0C\u83B7\u5F97\u63A9\u62A4\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_interruption1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - An enemy is using an interruption skill! He will act after a set number of
        your actions.
      - "\u67D0\u4E2A\u654C\u4EBA\u6B63\u5728\u4F7F\u7528\u6253\u65AD\u6280\u80FD\uFF01\u5728\u4F60\u884C\u52A8\u4E86\u7279\u5B9A\u6B21\u6570\u4E4B\u540E\uFF0C\u654C\u4EBA\u5C06\u4F1A\u884C\u52A8\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_interruption2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Moving or using a skill counts as 1 action, so plan carefully. Move Armand
        out of the interruption attack range.
      - "\u79FB\u52A8\u6216\u4F7F\u7528\u6280\u80FD\u90FD\u7B97\u4F5C 1 \u6B21\u884C\u52A8\uFF0C\u6240\u4EE5\u4F60\u8981\u8C28\u614E\u89C4\u5212\u3002\u5C06\u963F\u66FC\u5FB7\u79FB\u51FA\u6253\u65AD\u653B\u51FB\u7684\u8303\u56F4\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_interruption3
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - After your next action, the bandit will attack. Move Brunn out of the area.
      - "\u5728\u4F60\u4E0B\u4E00\u6B21\u884C\u52A8\u8FC7\u540E\uFF0C\u571F\u532A\u5C06\u4F1A\u653B\u51FB\u3002\u5C06\u5E03\u9C81\u6069\u79FB\u51FA\u8BE5\u533A\u57DF\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_position1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Select Brunn's Uppercut.
      - "\u9009\u62E9\u5E03\u9C81\u6069\u7684\u4E0A\u52FE\u62F3\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_position2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Melee attacks can hit from any angle. Hold CTRL and move Brunn to the target
        spot.
      - "\u8FD1\u6218\u653B\u51FB\u53EF\u4EE5\u4ECE\u4EFB\u4F55\u89D2\u5EA6\u547D\u4E2D\u3002\u957F\u6309
        CTRL \u952E\uFF0C\u5C06\u5E03\u9C81\u6069\u79FB\u52A8\u81F3\u76EE\u6807\u6240\u5728\u4F4D\u7F6E\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_arcanist1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Select the Arcane Spark skill.
      - "\u9009\u62E9\u5965\u672F\u706B\u82B1\u6280\u80FD\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_arcanist2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Enemies can also take cover, so now the chance to hit is too low.
      - "\u654C\u4EBA\u4E5F\u53EF\u4EE5\u5BFB\u627E\u63A9\u62A4\u3002\u6240\u4EE5\u53EF\u4EE5\u770B\u5230\uFF0C\u73B0\u5728\u7684\u547D\u4E2D\u51E0\u7387\u592A\u4F4E\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_arcanist3
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Target a different enemy.
      - "\u6362\u4E00\u4E2A\u654C\u4EBA\u7784\u51C6\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_end
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - "Well done! You've mastered the foundations of Blightstone combat. Every
        move, every strike is yours to command. The real challenges are waiting\u2014stay
        sharp and keep your wits about you."
      - "\u5E72\u5F97\u597D\uFF01\u4F60\u5DF2\u7ECF\u638C\u63E1\u4E86\u300A\u707E\u5384\u4E4B\u77F3\u300B\u7684\u6218\u6597\u57FA\u7840\u3002\u6BCF\u4E00\u6B21\u884C\u52A8\u3001\u6BCF\u4E00\u6B21\u8FDB\u653B\u90FD\u7531\u4F60\u6307\u6325\u5B9A\u593A\u3002\u771F\u6B63\u7684\u6311\u6218\u5C31\u5728\u524D\u65B9\u3002\u8BF7\u4FDD\u6301\u8B66\u89C9\uFF0C\u660E\u667A\u51B3\u65AD\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_combat2_xander
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Good job! Let me enhance the crystal with this gem.
      - "\u5E72\u5F97\u6F02\u4EAE\uFF01\u6211\u4F1A\u7528\u8FD9\u5757\u5B9D\u77F3\u6765\u5F3A\u5316\u6C34\u6676\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/CAMPFIRE 1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - 
      - 
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_campfire_init
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - At night, the Blighted Mist appears. The heroes light a campfire (costs 1
        wood) and eat (1 food per hero).
      - "\u665A\u4E0A\u4F1A\u51FA\u73B0\u707E\u5384\u8FF7\u96FE\u3002\u82F1\u96C4\u53EF\u4EE5\u751F\u8D77\u7BDD\u706B\uFF08\u6D88\u8017
        1 \u6728\u6750\uFF09\uFF0C\u7136\u540E\u5403\u4E9B\u4E1C\u897F\uFF08\u6BCF\u4F4D\u82F1\u96C4\u6D88\u8017
        1 \u98DF\u7269\uFF09\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_campfire_actionPoints
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Heroes have 3 campfire APs, and the crystal has 1 AP.
      - "\u82F1\u96C4\u6709 3 \u7BDD\u706B AP\uFF0C\u6C34\u6676\u6709 1 AP\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_campfire_blightedMist1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - As you approach the rift, the Blighted Mist worsens each night, raising the
        chance of dark events.
      - "\u968F\u7740\u4F60\u8D8A\u6765\u8D8A\u63A5\u8FD1\u88C2\u9699\uFF0C\u707E\u5384\u8FF7\u96FE\u7684\u5F71\u54CD\u5C06\u6108\u53D1\u4E25\u91CD\uFF0C\u591C\u95F4\u53D1\u751F\u6697\u9ED1\u4E8B\u4EF6\u7684\u51E0\u7387\u4E5F\u5C06\u968F\u4E4B\u4E0A\u5347\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_campfire_blightedMist2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Use 1 wood to light the fire, reducing the chance of dark events by 10%.
        You can do this up to 3 times per night.
      - "\u4F7F\u7528 1 \u6728\u6750\u751F\u706B\uFF0C\u53EF\u4EE5\u4F7F\u6697\u9ED1\u4E8B\u4EF6\u7684\u53D1\u751F\u51E0\u7387\u964D\u4F4E
        10%\u3002\u6B64\u64CD\u4F5C\u6BCF\u665A\u6700\u591A\u8FDB\u884C 3 \u6B21\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_campfire_sleep
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Choose and use wisely the skills you have, and when you're done, click Sleep.
      - "\u6B63\u786E\u9009\u62E9\u5E76\u4F7F\u7528\u6280\u80FD\u3002\u505A\u5B8C\u8BE5\u505A\u7684\u4E8B\u540E\uFF0C\u70B9\u51FB\u201C\u7761\u89C9\u201D\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: tutorial/tut_campfire_corruption
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Even with the crystal's protection, the Blighted Mist gives all heroes 8
        Blight points. At 25/50/75 points, they become Tainted/Deranged/Fractured.
      - "\u5373\u4FBF\u82F1\u96C4\u62E5\u6709\u6C34\u6676\u7684\u5E87\u62A4\uFF0C\u4E5F\u4ECD\u7136\u4F1A\u53D7\u5230\u707E\u5384\u8FF7\u96FE\u65BD\u52A0\u7684
        8 \u8150\u5316\u503C\u3002\u800C\u5F53\u8150\u5316\u8FBE\u5230 25\u300150\u300175
        \u70B9\u65F6\uFF0C\u82F1\u96C4\u5219\u4F1A\u5206\u522B\u8FDB\u5165\u611F\u67D3\u3001\u7CBE\u795E\u9519\u4E71\u548C\u5F7B\u5E95\u5D29\u6E83\u72B6\u6001\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/store1_info
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - A lone merchant roams the region, pack heavy with wares.
      - "\u4E00\u4E2A\u5546\u4EBA\u5728\u6B64\u5730\u72EC\u81EA\u6E38\u8361\uFF0C\u8EAB\u540E\u80CC\u7740\u6C89\u7538\u7538\u7684\u8D27\u7269\u3002"
