      - '{pensive}Anything they hid would be useless for us.'
      - "{pensive}\u4E0D\u7BA1\u4ED6\u4EEC\u85CF\u4E86\u4EC0\u4E48\uFF0C\u6211\u4EEC\u90FD\u7528\u4E0D\u4E0A\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/wealthyWell_leave_2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
