      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_info
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - Villagers under attack by feral beasts and their druid is missing. They desperately
        need help.
      - "\u6751\u6C11\u6B63\u5728\u906D\u53D7\u91CE\u517D\u7684\u88AD\u51FB\uFF0C\u800C\u4ED6\u4EEC\u7684\u5FB7\u9C81\u4F0A\u4E0B\u843D\u4E0D\u660E\u3002\u8FD9\u4E9B\u4EBA\u8FEB\u5207\u9700\u8981\u63F4\u52A9\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_start_1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{sad}Help! Please, help us!'
      - "{sad}\u6551\u547D\uFF01\u6551\u6551\u6211\u4EEC\u5427\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_start_2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}We need to help them. Let''s get their attention.'
      - "{positive}\u5F97\u53BB\u6551\u4ED6\u4EEC\u3002\u6211\u4EEC\u53BB\u5F15\u5F00\u91CE\u517D\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_start_3
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{taunt}HEY, YOU, LITTLE BEASTS!'
      - "{taunt}\u563F\uFF0C\u5C0F\u755C\u751F\uFF0C\u8FD9\u8FB9\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_start_4
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Get inside, quick!'
      - "{positive}\u8D76\u5FEB\u8FDB\u53BB\uFF01"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_start_5
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}These wolves are completely rabid.'
      - "{pensive}\u8FD9\u4E9B\u72FC\u90FD\u53D1\u72C2\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_combat_1
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}You saved us... thank you, truly.'
      - "{positive}\u8C22\u8C22\u4F60\u4EEC\u6551\u4E86\u6211\u4EEC......"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_combat_2
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}Please, take this. It''s the least we can do.'
      - "{positive}\u8BF7\u6536\u4E0B\u8FD9\u4E2A\u5427\uFF0C\u6211\u4EEC\u53EA\u80FD\u4EE5\u6B64\u6765\u8868\u8FBE\u8C22\u610F\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_combat_3
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{pensive}What was that about? Does that happen often?'
      - "{pensive}\u8FD9\u662F\u600E\u4E48\u56DE\u4E8B\uFF1F\u7ECF\u5E38\u53D1\u751F\u8FD9\u79CD\u4E8B\u5417\uFF1F"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_combat_4
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{sad}Too often. Lately, it feels like the whole forest is turning against
        us.'
      - "{sad}\u662F\u7684\uFF0C\u6700\u8FD1\u4EFF\u4F5B\u6574\u4E2A\u68EE\u6797\u90FD\u53D8\u6210\u4E86\u6211\u4EEC\u7684\u654C\u4EBA\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_combat_5
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{sad}But it wasn''t like this before... The animals used to keep to themselves.'
      - "{sad}\u4F46\u4EE5\u524D\u4E0D\u662F\u8FD9\u6837\u7684......\u4EE5\u524D\u52A8\u7269\u4EEC\u90FD\u5F88\u5B89\u5206\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_combat_6
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - "{positive}Aeryn always made sure of it. She's a druid\u2014lives deep in
        the forest"
      - "{positive}\u57C3\u7433\u4E00\u76F4\u8D1F\u8D23\u8FD9\u4E9B\u4E8B\uFF0C\u5979\u662F\u4E2A\u5FB7\u9C81\u4F0A\uFF0C\u4F4F\u5728\u68EE\u6797\u6DF1\u5904\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_combat_7
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{sad}She kept the wilds in balance. But no one''s seen her in days.'
      - "{sad}\u5979\u4E00\u76F4\u7EF4\u6301\u7740\u68EE\u6797\u7684\u79E9\u5E8F\uFF0C\u4F46\u6211\u4EEC\u6709\u597D\u51E0\u5929\u6CA1\u89C1\u8FC7\u5979\u4E86\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
    - Term: moor/unlockDruid_q1_combat_8
      TermType: 0
      Description: 
      Languages:
      - '{positive}We''ll look into it. If Aeryn''s in trouble, she might need our
        help.'
      - "{positive}\u6211\u4EEC\u4F1A\u7559\u610F\u8FD9\u4EF6\u4E8B\u3002\u5982\u679C\u57C3\u7433\u78B0\u4E0A\u9EBB\u70E6\uFF0C\u6211\u4EEC\u4F1A\u5E2E\u52A9\u5979\u7684\u3002"
      Flags: 0000
      Languages_Touch: []
